{"tid":1335621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進階防棍教學","createTime":"2019-07-20T15:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:04:12.000Z","uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42ee38944fee139a59a30167a34bb6c458241361","tid":1335621,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"有睇開片就會見到揮棍係要先拉弓再向下揮，幅度愈大傷害愈重，但每一次拉弓揮棍其實都要時間，當一拉弓就會出現硬直，弱點就係腋下，左手盾又擋唔到，如果畀遮篤中而力度夠大，係好易會甩棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31042fd9e20e37c94dbd7e9f6ae00aa250afb9c9","tid":1335621,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:03:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保障同行手足<br />\n向偽警說不！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【7.21有人冒警】和理非對偽警說不！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335553</a>"},{"pid":"b54754e5d71c84b6479de62cb2ebb51adf09b32e","tid":1335621,"uid":160605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"防警棍好簡單，同警犬有同樣裝備，用盾擋佢上身，然後用棍打佢腳"}]}